00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:19,600
 and I got a lot of console logs, et cetera.

245
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:23,400
 And if you're doing something like react or a review

246
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:26,480
 or some kind of a progressive web application,

